{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The demo of the game is an advanced prototypes with combat and story snippets. <br>In this demo : experience the beginnings of the story between Ikarus and Phi, explore the first floors and survive until the first boss!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2885250/extras/dt_boss_frame.gif?t=1727568009\" />DeathTower is a 2.5D isometric roguelite tactical RPG. Make your way through each floor and ascend to the top of the megastructure. But be careful along the way, or your body may be destroyed, forcing you to restart the adventure from the beginning!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2885250/extras/dt_push_frame.gif?t=1727568009\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Versatile Floor-by-Floor Progression</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine stealthy infiltration and an arsenal of devastating weapons to reach your objective. Melee weapons, special attacks, heavy artillery...There's no shortage of options, but you'll have to make some hard decisions\u2013you can't take everything with you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2885250/extras/dt_gunfight_frame.gif?t=1727568009\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hack the Tower</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Built thousands of years ago, the tower is home to countless mysteries. It operates autonomously, but you can also reprogram it to cover your escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2885250/extras/dt_hack_frame.gif?t=1727568009\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">An Ever-Changing World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the forbidden levels of the megastructure. Though officially empty, they each have their own e